title: Complete Stephen King
description:
This torrent contains every comic ever published with content by Stephen King.

Contents:



1981 - The Lawnmower Man (Marvel - Bizarre Adventures 29)

1982 - Stephen King's Creepshow (Plume)

1985 - Heroes for Hope (Marvel)

1992 - Popsy (Innovation Books - Masques 02)

2007-2013  - The complete The Dark Tower - The Gunslinger (Marvel)

2008-2011  - The complete The Stand (Marvel)

2009 - The Talisman Road of Trials 0-5 (Dell Rey Comics)

2010 - American Vampire 1-5 (Vertigo)

2010 - Stephen King's N 1-5 (Marvel)

2011 - Orbit - Stephen King (Bluewater Comics)

2012 - Road Rage 1-2 (IDW)



Thanks to the original uploader.
